---
title: "Зураг 3.4. Хэрэглэгчийн асуултад хариулах дарааллын диаграм"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 👤 Хэрэглэгч
    participant FE as ChatPage<br/>(React)
    participant API as api.js<br/>sendChat()
    participant Route as POST /api/chat<br/>(routes.py)
    participant Svc as ChatService<br/>process_query()
    participant Clf as Classifier<br/>predict()
    participant RAG as RAGPipeline<br/>search()
    participant Emb as EmbeddingManager
    participant FAISS as FAISS Index
    participant Gen as AnswerGenerator<br/>generate()
    participant Ollama as Ollama LLM<br/>:11434
    participant DB as SQLite<br/>chat_logs

    User->>FE: асуулт + Enter
    FE->>API: sendChat(message, category)
    API->>Route: POST /api/chat<br/>JSON
    Route->>Route: Pydantic validate
    Route->>Svc: process_query(query, category)

    Note over Svc: Step 1a: Identity shortcut
    Svc->>Svc: _is_identity_question?
    alt match
        Svc-->>Route: _IDENTITY_RESPONSE
    end

    Note over Svc: Step 1b: Capability shortcut
    Svc->>Svc: _is_capability_question?
    alt match
        Svc-->>Route: _CAPABILITY_RESPONSE
    end

    Note over Svc: Step 2: Greeting
    alt query in _GREETINGS
        Svc-->>Route: _GREETING_RESPONSE
    end

    Note over Svc: Step 3: Safety classification
    Svc->>Clf: predict(query)
    Clf->>Clf: clean + TF-IDF transform
    Clf->>Clf: model.predict_proba
    Clf-->>Svc: {label, confidence, is_safe}

    Note over Svc: Step 4: Crisis downgrade
    Svc->>Svc: _has_crisis_indicator?

    alt unsafe
        Svc->>DB: INSERT chat_logs
        Svc-->>Route: SAFETY_RESPONSES[label]
        Route-->>FE: ChatResponse + safety
        FE-->>User: Safety warning + хариу
    end

    Note over Svc: Step 5: Vague check
    alt query vague OR len ≤ 5
        Svc-->>Route: _CLARIFICATION_RESPONSE
    end

    Note over Svc: Step 6: RAG retrieval
    Svc->>RAG: search(prefix + query)
    RAG->>Emb: embed_query
    Emb-->>RAG: (1, 384) float32
    RAG->>FAISS: IndexFlatIP search
    FAISS-->>RAG: scores + indices
    RAG->>RAG: filter ≥0.3, FAQ boost +0.12, sort
    RAG-->>Svc: top-k chunks

    alt retrieved empty
        Svc-->>Route: _UNCLEAR_INTENT
    end

    Note over Svc: Step 7: Generation
    Svc->>Gen: generate(query, chunks)
    Gen->>Gen: format_sources

    alt FAQ fast-path (score ≥ 0.55)
        Gen-->>Svc: faq_answer
    else
        Gen->>Ollama: GET /api/tags (health)
        Gen->>Ollama: POST /api/chat<br/>system + context + query
        alt timeout 90s
            Gen-->>Svc: source_fallback
        else success
            Ollama-->>Gen: {content, eval_count}
            Gen->>Gen: clean citation header
            Gen-->>Svc: {answer, sources, tokens}
        end
    end

    Svc->>Svc: _looks_like_raw_snippet?
    Svc->>DB: INSERT chat_logs
    DB-->>Svc: chat_id
    Svc-->>Route: response dict
    Route-->>FE: ChatResponse JSON
    FE-->>User: Хариу + sources + feedback

    Note over User,DB: Optional feedback
    User->>FE: 👍 / 👎
    FE->>API: submitFeedback(chat_id, rating)
    API->>Route: POST /api/feedback
    Route->>DB: INSERT feedback
